{"_id":"0e0e480ad9f44866","name":"Digisoul Strike","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+)","description":"The Tamer with this class may use their Basic Action to make a melee attack against one adjacent enemy. This is a PR 2 attack. For every point of damage dealt, the Tamer gains 1 Hope immediately. This ability replaces long rest Hope recovery entirely. The Tamer with this class does not gain Hope from a long rest. Digisoul Strike is the only source of Hope generation unless another ability states otherwise. Digisoul Strike has no per-encounter limit. It can be used every turn."}}
{"_id":"122c6c1096663092","name":"Open Season","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Exposed, Knowledge rank 5","description":"The Marked Target now takes +2 additional damage from every attack made by any allied Digimon, not just the partner. The bonuses from Exposed and Open Season do not stack â€” the total bonus is +2 regardless of how many allied Digimon are attacking."}}
{"_id":"14942d00f05d5983","name":"Calculated Destruction","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Knowledge rank 7","description":"The flat +2 damage bonus on the Marked Target is replaced entirely. The Marked Target now takes additional damage equal to the Tamer's Knowledge rank from every attack made by any allied Digimon."}}
{"_id":"16df983cfedf9ca0","name":"Stronger Strike","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Digisoul Strike, Courage rank 4","description":"Digisoul Strike becomes a PR 4 attack. The Hope generation rate does not change."}}
{"_id":"21a08f0b53d6a21a","name":"Two Who Are One","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Courage rank 7 and Sincerity rank 7","description":"Once per session at the start of the Tamer's turn, they may activate Two Who Are One. Until the end of the encounter: Pack Instinct's bonus increases to +4. Feral Coordination no longer requires both to be within 1 space â€” its range extends to the Tamer's Sincerity rank in spaces. Whenever either the Tamer or their partner Digimon is healed, the other also restores HP equal to half the amount healed (rounded down)."}}
{"_id":"265ccdb5f48533b6","name":"I Know Who I Am","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Worth Protecting, Love rank 5","description":"The Tamer with this class is immune to social skill checks made against them by hostile Digimon. Additionally once per session when a Digimon NPC is hostile to the party, the Tamer may make a Sincerity check DN 14 as a Basic Action. On a success the Digimon's disposition shifts from hostile to neutral for the rest of the scene."}}
{"_id":"2a8996b17d27685e","name":"Any Time","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Not Yet, Love rank 5","description":"Open the Door can now be used off-turn as a Free Action â€” not just on the Tamer's own turn. Once per round regardless of whose turn it is."}}
{"_id":"448f82a9e18dd387","name":"Cover","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Love rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter when an allied Tamer or Digimon is hit by an attack, the Tamer with this class may use their Free Action off-turn to reduce the damage dealt by their Love rank."}}
{"_id":"4fe9e4f993a6aaae","name":"Calculated Movement","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Knowledge rank 3+)","description":"The Tamer with this class gains bonus movement each turn equal to their Knowledge rank in squares. This is in addition to their normal movement and does not consume any action."}}
{"_id":"526c6805663f190a","name":"Presence","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Calculated Disruption, Knowledge rank 5","description":"Once per encounter when the Tamer with this class ends their movement, all allied Digimon adjacent to them immediately recover HP equal to half the Tamer's current Hope total, rounded down."}}
{"_id":"59fa53b395c1ed29","name":"Pack Instinct","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+ and Sincerity rank 3+)","description":"While the Tamer with this class is within 1 space of their partner Digimon, the partner gains +2 to all attack rolls. The bonus drops immediately if the Tamer moves further away."}}
{"_id":"64b62dddff1d6ab2","name":"Common Ground","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (2+ Origin abilities, Love rank 3+)","description":"When the Tamer with this class makes a social skill check against a hostile Digimon, they gain a bonus equal to their Sincerity rank. They grew up among Digimon. That is not something that goes away."}}
{"_id":"6894cbc64e5df567","name":"Cover II","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Cover, Love rank 4","description":"Cover may now be used twice per encounter instead of once."}}
{"_id":"6a2a9551771ac664","name":"Feral Coordination","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Pack Instinct, Courage rank 4","description":"While Pack Instinct's bonus is active, once per encounter when the partner Digimon hits with an attack, the Tamer with this class may immediately follow up as a Free Action with a Brawl check DN 10 against the same target. On a success the target is Slowed until the end of their next turn. On a failure nothing additional happens."}}
{"_id":"76234106fd9cfe14","name":"All of It","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Love rank 7","description":"Once per session the Tamer with this class may give up their entire turn. Two allied Tamers of their choice each immediately take a full bonus turn with all of their normal actions available. These bonus turns resolve one at a time in the order the Tamer with this class chooses. The Tamer with this class takes no actions this round."}}
{"_id":"84e303743b87470e","name":"Not Yet","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Open the Door, Love rank 4","description":"Once per encounter when an enemy declares an attack against an allied Tamer, the Tamer with this class may use Open the Door off-turn to give that allied Tamer a Free Action before the attack resolves."}}
{"_id":"896945eebbf91288","name":"Shut Down","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Cover II, Love rank 5","description":"When the Tamer with this class uses Cover, the attacker loses their Move Action on their next turn."}}
{"_id":"9568aae6a1903267","name":"Hotter","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Raw Digisoul, Courage rank 5","description":"Digisoul Strike generates 3 Hope per damage dealt instead of 2."}}
{"_id":"99c2f13342a92819","name":"Mark Target","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Knowledge rank 3+)","description":"The Tamer with this class designates one visible enemy as the Marked Target. That enemy's current HP total is immediately revealed to all allies and updates visibly whenever it changes. The Mark can be transferred to a different visible enemy as a Free Action on the Tamer's turn. Only one enemy can be Marked at a time. The Mark lasts until the target is defeated or the encounter ends."}}
{"_id":"9cc46bbce03bd24d","name":"Distrust of Rules","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 1 ability, Sincerity rank 4","description":"Once per encounter when the Tamer with this class is targeted by a social skill check from an NPC â€” an attempt to intimidate, deceive, or persuade them â€” they may make a free Sincerity check DN 10 to recognise the attempt. On a success the check automatically fails."}}
{"_id":"a3c6e21a7a306fe9","name":"Worth Protecting","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"I Can Learn This, Love rank 4","description":"Once per session when the party is in a non-combat social situation, the Tamer with this class may spend a Free Action to draw on their history. The GM grants the party one piece of information about the current situation they would not otherwise have â€” a Digimon's true motive, a hidden danger, or a fact that changes how they approach what comes next."}}
{"_id":"a4f253e2373f9510","name":"Double Digisoul Burst","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 abilities, Courage rank 7","description":"Digisoul Strike becomes a PR 6 attack and generates 3 Hope per damage dealt. These values replace any previous PR and Hope rate from earlier rows. Once per session at the start of the Tamer's turn, they may declare Double Digisoul Burst. This turn Digisoul Strike costs no action â€” it is a Free Action in addition to any other actions the Tamer takes. When this Free Action hit lands, the partner Digimon immediately gains temporary HP equal to the total Hope generated by that single hit."}}
{"_id":"a879e662515107ae","name":"Not Your Enemy","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"At least 1 Row 2 ability, Sincerity rank 5","description":"Once per session when a wild or neutral Digimon would initiate combat against the party, the Tamer with this class may attempt to communicate with them before the encounter begins. Make a Sincerity check DN 13. On a success the Digimon pauses â€” the encounter does not begin and the GM determines their response. On a failure combat proceeds as normal."}}
{"_id":"aa15ddaaab8093ae","name":"Harder","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Stronger Strike, Courage rank 5","description":"Digisoul Strike becomes a PR 5 attack. Additionally whenever Digisoul Strike scores a critical hit, the total Hope generated by that hit is doubled."}}
{"_id":"af3961b9a506bb0a","name":"Raw Digisoul","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Marcus","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Digisoul Strike, Courage rank 4","description":"Digisoul Strike generates 2 Hope per damage dealt instead of 1. The PR does not change."}}
{"_id":"bc5f0715f086653c","name":"Raised Wild","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Courage rank 3+ and Sincerity rank 3+)","description":"Once per encounter when the Tamer with this class fails a skill check while in the Digital World, they may immediately reroll it using Sincerity instead of the original stat."}}
{"_id":"bf0578862b0dd8fd","name":"Open the Door","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Yoshino","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (Love rank 3+)","description":"Once per round on the Tamer's turn, one allied Tamer of their choice may immediately take a Free Action as if it were their own turn. This does not consume that ally's Free Action for the round."}}
{"_id":"c24ea6ef6760198d","name":"Calculated Disruption","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Calculated Movement, Knowledge rank 4","description":"When the Tamer with this class uses their bonus movement to enter a space adjacent to an enemy, that enemy loses their next Free Action. An enemy can only be disrupted this way once per encounter."}}
{"_id":"cf94c84b6333a73b","name":"Reach Them","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Digital Origin)","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Feral Coordination, Courage rank 5","description":"Once per session the Tamer with this class may spend their Basic Action to reach out to a corrupted allied Digimon. Make a Sincerity check DN 13. On a success the Digimon dedigivolves one stage and loses the corruption status immediately. On a failure the attempt has no effect and cannot be tried again this session on the same Digimon."}}
{"_id":"d31feba2970c9266","name":"Bridge Between Worlds","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Common Ground, Love rank 4","description":"The bonus from Common Ground now extends to all allied Tamers making social skill checks against hostile Digimon in the same interaction. The Tamer with this class speaks first and the door opens for everyone behind them."}}
{"_id":"d9d1caad96df9ecd","name":"I Can Learn This","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":1,"expCost":300,"requirements":"Entry requirement met (2+ Origin abilities, Love rank 3+)","description":"Once per session when the Tamer with this class fails a skill check involving human social interaction â€” Broadcast, Negotiate, or a similar context-specific check â€” they do not simply fail. They earn a free retry later this session on a comparable check with +2 to the roll."}}
{"_id":"e4678ba0181039b8","name":"Two Worlds, One Heart","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":3,"expCost":700,"requirements":"Bridge Between Worlds, Love rank 5","description":"Once per encounter the Tamer with this class may spend 4 Hope as a Free Action to grant both themselves and their partner Digimon resistance to the next hit that would reduce either of them below half their current HP. That hit deals half its damage to whichever of them it targets."}}
{"_id":"e58c5e333111d49a","name":"Exposed","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Thomas","row":2,"expCost":500,"requirements":"Mark Target, Knowledge rank 4","description":"The Marked Target takes +2 additional damage from every attack made by the Tamer's partner Digimon."}}
{"_id":"fe05d8a66fc169ac","name":"The Boy Who Came Home","type":"classSkill","img":"icons/svg/ability.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"system":{"class":"Keenan (Redeemed)","row":4,"expCost":1000,"requirements":"Both Row 3 Redeemed abilities, Love rank 7","description":"Once per session at the start of the Tamer's turn, they may activate this ability. All allied Tamers and Digimon currently on the field gain temporary HP equal to this Tamer's Love rank Ã— 2. For the rest of this encounter the Sincerity rank bonus from Common Ground applies to all social checks the party makes â€” not just those against hostile Digimon."}}
